                "text": "Once per day, a malenti that takes damage in combat can fly into a frenzy in the following round. It gains a +2 bonus to its Constitution and Strength, but takes a \u20132 penalty to its AC. The frenzy lasts as long as the battle or 1 minute, whichever is shorter."
